                    <placeName key="ed_ubz_2cl_3y">Manchester</placeName></correspAction></correspDesc></profileDesc><revisionDesc><listChange><change><date>2018-03-14T09:46:28Z</date> | <name>Sascha Grabsch</name> | <orgName>Telota</orgName> | OxGarage DOCX to TEI | 2.15.0</change><change><date>2018-03-14T15:34:57+01:00</date> | <name>Sascha Grabsch</name> | <orgName>Telota</orgName> | convert_tei_file.py | 0.85</change></listChange></revisionDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div type="writingSession">
                <opener>
                    <dateline><pb/> Aug 21<hi rendition="#sup">st
                        </hi>1867</dateline>
                    <salute>Dear Engels</salute>
                </opener>
                <p><seg type="comment"><orig>I should be glad to see
                            you.</orig><note xml:id="d9ae230f-7ffe-486a-8155-9a7f82d32f5f">Siehe
                            auch <ref target="B00328"><?oxy_comment_start author="reichhoff" timestamp="20180523T132214+0200" comment="(Br. 319)"?>W.
                                H. Claus an Engels, 22.8.1867<?oxy_comment_end?></ref>
                            (Br. 319).</note></seg> Just returned from Africa. <seg type="comment"><orig>Called upon <persName key="pdrPo.001.004.000001969">Gumpert</persName> but find him absent.</orig><note xml:id="e1ae6782-3591-4c12-a28f-c0b27d22f0ad"><persName key="pdrPo.001.004.000001969">Eduard Gumpert</persName> kam etwa
                            Ende August – Anfang September 1867 nach Manchester zurück (siehe <ref target="B00339"><?oxy_comment_start author="reichhoff" timestamp="20180523T132321+0200" comment="(Br. 330.22))."?>Engels
                                an Marx, 2.9.1867 <?oxy_comment_end?></ref>).</note></seg> Leaving
                    Manchester to-morrow again for Paris &amp; Germany. </p>
                <p><pb/> Will see you again after my return &amp; settle old
                    scores.</p>
                <closer>Yours very sincerely<lb/>W.H. Claus.</closer>
</div>
    <div type="writingSession">
        <p>In haste <pb/></p>
            </div></body></text></TEI>